></pre></div>\n<p>When you run the above code you will get the current day in your golang console, let‚Äôs check the output.</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 630px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/4835aca67989ad296a8914d2ef61ce8d/693cc/get-current-day-output.jpg\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 46.835443037974684%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"get, current day, golang\"\n        title=\"get, current day, golang\"\n        src=\"/static/4835aca67989ad296a8914d2ef61ce8d/828fb/get-current-day-output.jpg\"\n        srcset=\"/static/4835aca67989ad296a8914d2ef61ce8d/ff44c/get-current-day-output.jpg 158w,\n/static/4835aca67989ad296a8914d2ef61ce8d/a6688/get-current-day-output.jpg 315w,\n/static/4835aca67989ad296a8914d2ef61ce8d/828fb/get-current-day-output.jpg 630w,\n/static/4835aca67989ad296a8914d2ef61ce8d/0ede0/get-current-day-output.jpg 945w,\n/static/4835aca67989ad296a8914d2ef61ce8d/693cc/get-current-day-output.jpg 988w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 630px) 100vw, 630px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://onecompiler.com/go/3y3svazzz\" target=\"_BLANK\">Try it yourself</a></p>\n<p>All the best üëç</p>","frontmatter":{"title":"How to get current day in golang?","tags":["GoLang"],"date":"May 12, 2022","description":"Example of get current day in golang with step by step tutorial - aGuideHub","social_image":"..\\..\\static\\media\\template\